Authors: List of authors of the dataset
Acknowledgment: Acknowledgement of funding and help to generate the dataset
Dataset_DOI: Digital Object Identifier (DOI) associated with the dataset if the dataset was published
Publication_Citation: Full citation associated with the paper that uses the dataset
Lat: Latitude of the dataset site study in decimal units (Y)
Long: Longitude of the dataset site study in decimals units (X)
Elevation: Elevation of the dataset site study
